description:
Note that songs included are their respective abridged versions.

You must have the full version of the game to use this content. Additionally, you must be playing on the latest version of the game to access the content.

Songs included:
- BOKUTACHIWA TENSHIDATTA
- CHA-LA  HEAD-CHA-LA 
- DAN DAN KOKORO HIKARETEKU
- DETEKOI TOBIKIRI ZENKAI POWER
- KYOUFUNO GINYUU TOKUSENTAI
- MAKAFUSHIGI ADVENTURE
- NEW HERO TOUJOU
- PROLOGUE & SUBTITLE 1
- ROMANTIC AGERUYO
- SOLID STATE SCOUTER
- WE GOTTA POWER
name: Super Dragon Ball Heroes: World Mission Anime Music Pack 1
